A common [customisation request](http://webconverger.com/buy/) is to disable
the [[boot_menu|boot]] prompt, in order to:

* Make boots quicker
* Disallow any [[boot]] time alterations

This is done by replacing the syslinux theme with `progress-appliance` in
[auto/config](http://anonscm.debian.org/gitweb/?p=debian-live/config-webc.git;a=blob;f=webconverger/auto/config;)
when [[building_Webconverger|develop]].

	--syslinux-theme progress-appliance

